---
// Header.astro - Sem links de navegação para corresponder exatamente ao layout minimalista do Figma
---

<header class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full z-50">
  <nav class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 py-6 md:py-8">
    <a href="/" class="text-white font-[var(--font-body)] text-base md:text-[17px] font-normal tracking-[0.06em] hover:opacity-85 transition-opacity">
      Aliine Souza Nail Design
    </a>

    <a
      href="#contato"
      class="bg-[var(--color-accent)] text-white text-sm md:text-[15px] font-medium px-6 py-2.5 rounded-[8px] hover:bg-[var(--color-accent-hover)] transition-colors shadow-sm"
    >
      Agendar meu horario
    </a>
  </nav>
</header>
